# Household CFO — Full Stack Build Prompt

## Project Overview

Build a balance sheet-first personal finance application for dual-income households and mid-career professionals. The app applies proper double-entry accrual accounting principles to give users a true household financial position — not just an expense tracker. The product is called **Household CFO**.

The core value proposition: show users their **true liquid position** — cash and near-cash assets minus accrued liabilities, outstanding credit balances, and provisioned upcoming obligations — in real time. This is the hero metric the entire product is built around.

