### Frontend
- **Framework:** Next.js 14 with App Router
- **Language:** TypeScript (strict mode)
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS
- **Components:** Shadcn/ui + Radix UI primitives
- **Charts:** Recharts for standard charts, D3.js for custom financial visualizations
- **State / Server State:** React Query (TanStack Query v5) for all server state
- **Forms:** React Hook Form + Zod validation
- **Supabase Client:** @supabase/ssr for server components and route handlers

### Backend / Infrastructure
- **Database:** Supabase (PostgreSQL)
- **Auth:** Supabase Auth with MFA (TOTP) enabled
- **Edge Functions:** Supabase Edge Functions (Deno, TypeScript)
- **Realtime:** Supabase Realtime for live balance sheet updates
- **Bank Connections:** Plaid (transactions, balances, account identity)
- **Document Parsing:** Edge Function that accepts PDF/CSV uploads and extracts financial data
- **Notifications:** Supabase Edge Functions + Resend (email) + Web Push (in-app/push)
- **Job Scheduling:** pg_cron extension in Supabase for daily accrual runs
- **Currency:** USD only
- **Offline:** Not required

