## Notification System

### In-App Notifications
Insert into notifications table. Frontend subscribes via Supabase Realtime to new rows where `user_id = auth.uid()`. NotificationBell component shows unread count badge. NotificationList renders all notifications with mark-as-read.

### Email Notifications
Use **Resend** as the email provider. Create transactional email templates for each notification type. The `send-notification` Edge Function calls the Resend API when `email_enabled = true` in user preferences.

### Push Notifications
Implement Web Push using the Web Push Protocol. Store push subscriptions in a `push_subscriptions` table. The `send-notification` Edge Function sends push payloads using the `web-push` library when `push_enabled = true`.

### Notification Types and Triggers

| Type | Trigger | Threshold |
|---|---|---|
| low_liquid_position | After any position recalculation | User-defined (default $1,000) |
| accrued_liability_threshold | After daily accrual run | User-defined (default $5,000) |
| missed_obligation | Obligation past due_date with no journal entry | Any |
| budget_review_reminder | pg_cron daily, checks day_of_month preference | User-defined day |
| monthly_close_reminder | pg_cron on 28th of month | Fixed |
| income_statement_ready | After period close completes | Automatic |
| net_worth_milestone | After balance sheet snapshot | User-defined milestones |
| balance_sheet_snapshot | After period close completes | Automatic |
| large_transaction | After Plaid webhook posts a transaction | User-defined (default $500) |
| account_connection_error | Plaid webhook receives error status | Any |
| manual_entry_posted | After manual journal entry is confirmed | Automatic |

